  "body": "### Description\r\nSupport setting a fixed base fee instead of using the EIP-1559 mechanism, returned by the BASEFEE opcode. It can be set to zero or a value such as 1.\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n* Basefee can be configured on hard fork.\r\n* Optionally, it can be overridden with a configuration flag.\r\n\r\nSee Mystique hard fork info: https://github.com/ethereumclassic/ECIPs/issues/432\r\n",
